task.summary: First BDD procedure passed with cucumber-rails training wheels. The training wheels should be removed soon.
Moving title generation logic to application_helper
Add validation on project name to ensure its presence before saving it to DB. All BDD steps with "projects" are done.
Added the ability to show all projects.
Added the ability to edit projects.
Added the ability to destroy projects. Basic CRUD for projects implemented.
Extracted project finding to the before_filter. Redirect 404 to projects_path. Changed some "key: val" pair to ":key => val" for readability's sake.

Changed production environment configuration of assets: config.serve_static_assets = false => true in order to make WEBrick server be able to serve precompiled CSS files.
NOTE: if the app is to be deployed to Apache or nginx servers, this configuration should be set to false.
Restrict access to project modification actions to admins only.
Changed Gemfile to meet the need of RubyMine debugging.
